data.title: Arlington Baptist Church
data.meta_description: Arlington Baptist Church is an independent Baptist church ministering to the needs of the northwest Baltimore, Maryland community. Our church family extends to surrounding areas including Randallstown, Ellicott City, Pikesville, Lochearn, Woodlawn, Hebbville, Woodstock, Catonsville, and more.
data.text:
TRAFFIC ALERT

Please be advised that traffic congestion is expected every Tuesday this summer between 9:00 AM and 5:00 PM.

Arlington Baptist Church is a group of ordinary people seeking an extraordinary God.

Whether you're a Christian looking for a church home, or you're full of questions about this man named Jesus, or you're somewhere in between, there's a place for you at ABC.

You'll find grace among friends at Arlington Baptist!
